record_data.record_title: Reactive Rate Schedule and Voltage Control
record_data.record_plain_text:
Reactive Supply and Voltage Control from Generation Sources Service
Martins Creek, LLC ( Martins Creek ) provides Reactive Supply and Voltage Control from Generation Sources Service ( Reactive Supply Service ) from various generating units in the PPL Zone to the PJM Interconnection, L.L.C. ( PJM ). This Rate Schedule consists of twenty-four separate tariff rate sections, one for each generating unit, and sets forth Martins Creek s revenue requirements for the provision of Reactive Supply Service to PJM within the PPL Zone consistent with Schedule 2 of the PJM Open Access Transmission Tariff. This Rate Schedule shall be effective on December 1, 2016.
Allentown CTG 1
1. TOTAL REVENUE REQUIREMENT
Total Annual Revenue Requirement is $8,555.86.
Total Monthly Revenue Requirement is $8,555.86 / 12 = $712.99.
